{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lively Chair Simulator is a game with freaky controls. In the game, you are moving a chair by controlling each of the legs of the chair individually. Sounds difficult, but walking is not the limit of a chair. They can run and maybe jump. Have a Try, it is free for now. See if you are suitable for being a chair.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It is not a WASD system, instead, it is a QWERASDFGH system, four for moving legs forward, four for moving legs backward, and two for abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It is important to have a basic understanding of the system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In single mode, there are some levels to let you get good control of the chair. Some chairs may not be suitable for passing all levels. After finishing the levels, you should know how to walk, run, upslope, upstairs, push boxes, and jump.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In multiplayer mode, there are six games. 15m Race and Seesaw games can be started with only one player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">15m Race</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2013 Just Run</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pushing Game </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u2013 The last one not touching the outside wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">StoneBall</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u2013 The first team reaches 10000 points wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2013 Earning points if public stoneball or your team target stoneball in range of your team pointing stoneball.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2013 Losing points if no team members are in range of your team pointing stoneball or any team stoneballs from the other team in range of your team pointing stoneball.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">6036</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2013 The time of the last person who touched the ball will be accumulated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2013 The game ends when someone's time reaches 60s.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2013 The one with the time closest to 36s wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Air Hockey</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2013 Just like air hockey</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Seesaw</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2013 The game ends if the seesaw hits the ground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2013 Getting points from pushing away the stone balls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2013 Losing points if you fall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u2013 7 different chairs </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u2013 12 levels </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u2013 Multiplayer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u2013 Achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u2013 Simple 3D Graphics</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A Good Start","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2575060/fdc83ab74b00d9305a9ca621d28867060e9baa38.jpg"},{"name":"Jump","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2575060/35ef170d578b751fe30c775c119c964932884ede.jpg"},{"name":"You Did It","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2575060/f494c00aa1d24826b985b4598d70502bfcde9a90.jpg"},{"name":"Run Very Fast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2575060/d2c865b406c23f62ba838d846b2d7d74e2e15641.jpg"},{"name":"Pushing King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2575060/9740f6626e4531140972c43f3483df53f50d7195.jpg"},{"name":"Run Extremely Fast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2575060/46905d8238f816ccba6b7f8550f2c49266e65a08.jpg"},{"name":"I Wish It Never Ends","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2575060/2937481ae22c46f566f809d7c5015cf7b3a66622.jpg"},{"name":"Small Support","path":"https:/